snippet.title: Clash: Artifacts of Chaos | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The creatures of Zenozoik are an odd lot, and no day in this surreal dreamscape is like any other. Even so, here's a look at one day in the life of Pseudo a hermit living on the fringes of society. But keep your wits about you as everything changes when darkness falls.

Pseudo's previously relatively peaceful days will be thrown into chaos when he meets the boy, a creature whose mysterious powers are the catalyst for an adventure that will change everything for the two of them. 

Clash: Artifacts of Chaos will be available in February 2023 on Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, and PC!
